text: 2026 (MMXXVI) will be a common year starting on Thursday in the Gregorian calendar, the 2026th year of the Common Era (CE) and Anno Domini (AD) designations, . ==Events== *2026 FIFA World Cup *2026 Winter Olympics *2026 Sarawak State Election *February 6–22 – The 2026 Winter Olympics are scheduled to be held in Milan and Cortina d'Ampezzo, Italy. *March 6–15 – The 2026 Winter Paralympics are scheduled to be held in Milan and Cortina d'Ampezzo, Italy. *March 17–29 – The 2026 Commonwealth Games are scheduled to be held in Victoria, Australia. *May – The 2026 Eurovision song contest is scheduled; the location is typically determined by the previous year's winner. *June - July 19 – The 2026 FIFA World Cup is scheduled to be held in the United States, Canada, and Mexico. *July 4 – The United States celebrates its 250th birthday (Semiquincentennial) === Date unknown === * November – Artemis 2, the second mission of the Artemis program, is planned to launch.
